Define CNN Model¶

In [20]:
def create_cnn_model_3conv(num_filters, filter_size, dropout_rate):

    model = models.Sequential()
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(num_filters, filter_size, activation='relu', input_shape=(32, 32, 3)))
    model.add(layers.Dropout(dropout_rate)) # Dropout katmanı ekledik
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(num_filters, filter_size, activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.Dropout(dropout_rate)) # Dropout katmanı ekledik
    model.add(layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)))
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(num_filters, filter_size, activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.Dropout(dropout_rate)) # Dropout katmanı ekledik
    model.add(layers.Flatten())
    model.add(layers.Dense(num_filters, activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.Dense(10, activation='softmax'))
    model.summary()
    
    return model
In [83]:
def create_cnn_model_5conv(num_filters, filter_size, dropout_rate):
    
    model = models.Sequential()
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(num_filters, filter_size, activation='relu', input_shape=(32, 32, 3)))
    model.add(layers.Dropout(dropout_rate)) # Dropout katmanı ekledik
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(num_filters, filter_size, activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.Dropout(dropout_rate)) # Dropout katmanı ekledik
    # model.add(layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)))
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(num_filters, filter_size, activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.Dropout(dropout_rate)) # Dropout katmanı ekledik
    model.add(layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2)))
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(num_filters, filter_size, activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.Dropout(dropout_rate)) # Dropout katmanı ekledik
    model.add(layers.Conv2D(num_filters, filter_size, activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.Dropout(dropout_rate)) # Dropout katmanı ekledik
    model.add(layers.Flatten())
    model.add(layers.Dense(num_filters, activation='relu'))
    model.add(layers.Dense(10, activation='softmax'))
    model.summary()
    
    return model

Visualise Loss and Accuracy for Train and Validation Set¶

In [5]:
def visualise_loss_and_accuracy(history):   
    # Modelin eğitimi sırasında kaydedilen loss ve accuracy değerleri
    train_loss = history.history['loss']
    val_loss = history.history['val_loss']
    train_accuracy = history.history['accuracy']
    val_accuracy = history.history['val_accuracy']
    
    # Loss grafiğini çizdirme
    plt.figure(figsize=(15, 3))
    plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
    plt.plot(train_loss, label='Training Loss', color='blue')
    plt.plot(val_loss, label='Validation Loss', color='orange')
    plt.title('Training and Validation Loss')
    plt.xlabel('Epoch')
    plt.ylabel('Loss')
    plt.legend()
    
    # Accuracy grafiğini çizdirme
    plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
    plt.plot(train_accuracy, label='Training Accuracy', color='blue')
    plt.plot(val_accuracy, label='Validation Accuracy', color='orange')
    plt.title('Training and Validation Accuracy')
    plt.xlabel('Epoch')
    plt.ylabel('Accuracy')
    plt.legend()
    
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

Visualise Confusion Matrix¶

In [6]:
def visualise_confusion_matrix(cm):
    # Class Names
    class_names = ['airplane', 'automobile', 'bird', 'cat', 'deer', 'dog', 'frog', 'horse', 'ship', 'truck']
    
    # Confusion matrix'i görselleştirelim
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))
    sns.heatmap(cm, annot=True, fmt='d', cmap='Blues', xticklabels=class_names, yticklabels=class_names)
    plt.xlabel('Tahmin Edilen Etiketler')
    plt.ylabel('Gerçek Etiketler')
    plt.title('Confusion Matrix')
    plt.show()
